While the gameplay is also fairly disappointing, it at least offers plenty of variety. Many of the gameÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢s hidden object scenes allow you to scroll from side to side to change your viewing angle, and youÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢ll then be asked to find items based either on their names in text (as is most traditional for the genre), or by looking for them based on small pictures or silhouettes.
